abstract: >-
  A comprehensive geospatial analysis project for automated land cover
  classification using Sentinel-2 satellite imagery and optimized spectral
  indices. This work implements machine learning-based optimization of BSI
  (Bare Soil Index) and NBI (New Built-up Index) using F1-score maximization
  for improved land cover detection in the Vijayawada region, India.
